"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/892270","Department for Education","false","2018-05-02","<p>The information requested is not held centrally.</p><p> </p>","Stratford-on-Avon","Nadhim Zahawi","138396","2018-05-02T16:40:38.473Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/892270/answer","Biography information for Nadhim Zahawi","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/892270/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/892270/answer","Stratford-on-Avon","Stratford-on-Avon","Nadhim Zahawi","Nadhim Zahawi","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/892270/answer/previousversion/55418","Biography information for Nadhim Zahawi","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/892270/answer/previousversion/55418","Biography information for Nadhim Zahawi","60","Education","Education","2018-04-26","Educational Psychology","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, what estimate he has made of the number of children who received help from schools-based educational psychologists in each of the last three years for which data is available.","false","Biography information for Chris Ruane","Vale of Clwyd","Chris Ruane","138395"
